      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. JESS SINFUL lines up for the first time since October 25. Started the last campaign impressively when in the placings over 229m at this track. Strong chance to kick the campaign off on the right note. 5. KEEP HER OFF TEQUILA is back after a break of six months. Went close to a maiden win before the layoff, finishing second at her latest appearance over 366m at Will Rogers Downs (Dirt). Ready to find winning form. 8. LAST FAMOUS EAGLE returns after six months in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a eighth over 320m at this track (Dirt). Rates highly and is a chance to break through. 11. LUNA UNLYMITED turned in a moderate debut over 302m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt) on March 19 when she was safely held in tenth, 7 lengths from the winner. Germarious A O'neal is a key engagement. Will take a lot from that experience. Don't underestimate.\",\"runners\":[3,5,8,11],\"exclusive\":false}",
